    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pamina VS Slimes is a fast-paced, top-down arcade action game. In this 10-minute minigame, you’ll take on endless waves of slimes invading your home.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4 playable characters: You can also headpat them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Elemental strategy: Mastering the elemental strengths and weaknesses will be  the key to overcoming your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Burst Skills: Get out of tricky situations with powerful burst skills!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 4 Game Modes: Test your skills across distinct modes, each offering its own challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a heated battle filled with action and fun!</p>",
